name: The Key to Victory
description:
You have to survive. Whatever happens, you have to survive.
Made for GMTKJam 2020 with theme "Out of Control"
Everything is created from scratch except 4 sound effects.

Press SPACE to go to next level or restart when the button appear.

Game by:
Ahmed Khalifa (@amidos2006)
Ray Robin Vermeulen - Landerack
Brother Android (@harrison_lemke)
